Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:44.67,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is such a sweet illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:46.07,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,let's come together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.08,0:00:50.45,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,can't seem to stop but my imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.46,0:00:51.79,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,goes on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:55.99,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a ridiculous situation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:57.45,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Another matter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:02.85,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't deny I'm faced with a tricky temptation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.86,0:01:05.16,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:08.18,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that keeps on changing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:10.54,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,don't know why
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:13.32,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my heart is aching
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:22.70,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta handle it no more hesitation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:25.64,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There can be no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:26.67,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,god only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:28.57,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mind is as free as the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:30.47,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:32.98,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what I should do is to fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:34.12,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,god only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:37.15,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need that kind of real things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:40.67,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like I am lost in the labyrinth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:41.57,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,god only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:44.54,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There must be the meaning of life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.58,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow unexpectedly happenings thrill me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:48.73,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,god only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:49.69,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,just believe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:50.68,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:52.73,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and my dream anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:55.28,OPRW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,could be a hero or heroine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:44.67,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛是如此美妙幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:46.07,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.08,0:00:50.45,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺思永不停息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.46,0:00:51.79,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限夢魘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:55.99,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:57.45,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是另一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:02.85,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我無法否認 面前這魅惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.86,0:01:05.16,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:08.18,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無常的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:10.54,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:13.32,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心痛不止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:22.70,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能面對 不再迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:25.64,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也無法回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:26.67,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有神知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:28.57,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心如風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:30.47,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:32.98,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要墜入愛河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:34.12,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有神知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:37.15,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要 世間的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:40.67,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同歧路亡羊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:41.57,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有神知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:44.54,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這必定是 生活的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.58,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撲面而來 讓我戰慄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:48.73,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有神知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:49.69,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:50.68,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我之名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:52.73,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我夢中 每人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:55.28,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能主演
