Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥 哥 哥哥大人 有什麼可以寫的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我簽 請讓我簽
