Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你獲得新人獎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要走的路還長呢
